cast.overview: Ebenezer Scrooge is far too greedy to understand that Christmas is a time for kindness and generosity. But with the guidance of some new found friends, Scrooge learns to embrace the spirit of the season. A retelling of the classic Dickens tale with Disney's classic characters.
cast.title: Mickey's Christmas Carol
cast.character: Jiminy Cricket - Ghost of Christmas Past (voice)

details.biography: Eddie Carroll was a Canadian-American actor and voice actor, who is best known as the third performer to provide the voice for Jiminy Cricket, a role he played for over 35 years.
details.name: Eddie Carroll
